Title: A trip to home
DateModified: '2018-01-19'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/a-trip-to-home
SetInCountry: India
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Khaja  Aqeel
AuthorCountry: India
Text: Well this story is based on a boy. Who's visiting his hometown after 10 years.
  The last he saw his home town was totally different. In order to fulfill his promise
  to his love. His hometown is Kashmir and he moved to New Delhi at the age of 15
  for his higher studies. He experiences totally bizarre incidents on his trip to
  home. He totally excited about his return so is his love.
